Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生了无尽膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天 新的发现都在揭秘这个诡异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼 神秘莫测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方 - 我们所谓的《宇宙》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电杆大小的棍棒从外太空飞驰而下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Telephone-pole-sized rods streak down from outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭地球上的目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and obliterate targets on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将是终极掩体克星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be the ultimate bunker buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强大的激光瞬间炸毁任何方向的敌人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Powerful lasers instantly blast enemies in any direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.16,0:00:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会在看到敌人启动武器的同时遭毒手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You'll get zapped at the same time that you see the zapper initiate the zapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹速度接近光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Missiles traveling near the speed of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生爆炸无需炸药\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}deliver massive blasts without the aid of explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它开始成为潜在的武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It starts to become possible to hit things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有核弹的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the energy of an atomic bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上不必用上任何辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without actually having to use any sort of radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员殊死搏斗在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And space pilots battle to the death
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全另类的空战中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a very different kind of dogfight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些不是科幻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These aren't just sci-fi fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是宇宙间未来的太空战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are the future of space wars in the universe.
