Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史频道 - 宇宙 第4季第8集 太空战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The History Channel - The Universe s04e08 Space Wars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后100年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's 100 years in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的边疆已经变成了终极战场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the final frontier has turned into the ultimate battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球上的歹徒殖民地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A rogue colony on the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经袭击了邻近的殖民地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has already attacked neighboring colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球派出的飞船已进入阵地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A spacecraft from Earth has moved into position
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时谈判已经破裂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}after negotiations have broken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着我们走入太阳系乃至外太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we travel out into the solar system and maybe even the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会有人与人之间的意见不合\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there are going to be people who disagree with other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜在的战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the potential for warfare 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与人类史上的任何时候一样大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is just as great there as it has been any time through human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歹徒殖民地夺走更多无辜生命之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Before the rogue colony takes any more innocent lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞船释放了无比强大的武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the spacecraft releases a weapon of unimaginable power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物质炸弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an anti-matter bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物质与普通物质并无两样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anti-matter is the same as normal matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了相反的原子电荷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}except with the opposite atomic charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非负电荷的电子和正电荷的质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Instead of negative electrons and positive protons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物质具有正电荷的电子和负电荷的质子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}anti-matter has positive electrons and negative protons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦物质与反物质接触\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When matter and anti-matter touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们就会瞬间同时湮灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they instantly annihilate each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生巨大的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}releasing a huge amount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你有反物质与物质碰撞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you have anti-matter colliding with matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的质量就会转换成能量 -\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all of the mass gets converted into energy--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分百的效率\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}100% efficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是回报大大的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's a lot of bang for the buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核武器甚至都只有约1%的效率\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even nuclear weapons are only about 1% efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学武器在效率方面可谓微乎其微\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Chemical weapons are a tiny fraction of a percent in terms of their efficiency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通物质的弹头在行将与内部的反物质接触时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A warhead of normal matter would simply explode
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会发生爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when it came in contact with the anti-matter inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞向歹徒殖民地的反物质炸弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The anti-matter bomb streaking toward the rogue colony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一团由电磁场所包围的反物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a mass of anti-matter surrounded by an electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在撞击之前 电磁场是关闭的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just before impact, the field is turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至都无需引信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't even need a fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要将反物质到达所需的目标并打击它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You just need that anti-matter to reach the desired destination and hit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后它就会转换其所有的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it will then convert all of its energy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及它所打击的目标的能量转换成爆炸的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the energy of the object that it hit into this explosive energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生巨大的爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}producing a tremendous explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕着地球的其它航天器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Other spacecraft in orbit around Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,则用强大的激光武器来攻击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}target smaller remote outposts loyal to the rogue colony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠于歹徒殖民地偏远的的小哨所\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with powerful laser weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光武器的优势\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}An advantage of a laser weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在于激光束的穿行达到了光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that the laser beam travels at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你可以将这些激光束在极端的时间里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you could have these light beams going across very large distances
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越遥远的距离 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a very small amount of time, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌人尚未意识到之前就消灭他们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}zapping the enemy before the enemy realizes what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光在宇宙间穿行的速度是每秒18 6万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Light races across the universe at 186,000 miles per second,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此未来在近地轨道上发射的激光武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so the futuristic laser weapons fired from orbit near Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要一秒钟就能对约24万英里远的月球上的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}take just over a second to blast holes in their targets on the Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标炸出一个窟窿来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about 240,000 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只是因为我们在未来的100年里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But just because we're 100 years in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不意味着简单的投射武器会从战场上消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}doesn't mean simple projectiles have disappeared from the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们通过猛烈轰击敌人施加危害\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They inflict damage by slamming into the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用所谓的动能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}using what's known as kinetic energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动之能 来摧毁目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the energy of motion, to destroy a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们将某种物质加速到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we accelerated some kind of mass
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光速的相当比例\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}up to sizable fractions of the speed of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至都无需弹头了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you wouldn't even need a warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时该物体本身运动的动能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just the kinetic energy of the motion of that object itself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就具有难以置信的破坏力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would have an incredible destructive power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小行星撞击行星一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like an asteroid impacting a planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物体的重量(质量)越大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the more an object weighs-- its mass--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它跑得(速度)越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the faster it's going-- its velocity--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么它所具有的动能就越大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the more kinetic energy it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过速度在动能方程式中 优势盖过了质量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But velocity has an advantage over mass in the kinetic energy equation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为质量要乘以速度的平方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}since mass is multiplied by the square of the velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此速度快上两倍的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So something traveling twice as fast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四倍于相同质量物体的动能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has four times the kinetic energy of something of equal mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你有很高速度的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you get something up to very high velocities,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它就具有大量的动能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it has a lot of kinetic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动能的差异是很容易看出的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The different amounts of kinetic energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用同样的弹丸来打击目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are easy to see when hitting a target with the same type of projectile
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而用上两种不同的速度的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}traveling at two different speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位火器专家将发射两个一米一样的铅弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This firearms expert is going to fire two identical lead balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先用上这支滑膛手枪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the first from this smooth-bore pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是用这支滑膛火枪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the second from this smooth-bore musket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于其枪膛更长 火药填量更多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, with its longer barrel and larger powder charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它发射的弹丸将要快更多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's going to fire that ball much faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 手枪把弹丸送向靶子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}First, the pistol sends the ball downrange 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对较慢的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at a relatively slow speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在火枪发射同样大小的弹丸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now the musket fires the same sized lead ball
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度较快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at a higher speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在靶子的背后 你可以看到手枪射出的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On the back of the target, you can see the damage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹丸所造成的危害\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}caused by the lead ball fired from the pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在来看看火枪射出的弹丸造成的结果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But now look at what happened with the lead ball from the musket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动能高多了 危害也大多了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Much higher kinetic energy, much greater damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真空状态的太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And out in the vacuum of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有大气让物体减速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's no atmosphere to slow things down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而地球轨道上的另一艘飞船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So another ship in Earth orbit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一个由高密度金属制成的电杆大小的炮弹射向\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}launches a telephone-pole-sized projectile made of dense metal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒殖民地的地下司令部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the rogue colonists' underground headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被称为上帝之棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's known as a rod from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过短暂的火箭推进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After a brief rocket boost,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力加速度让非爆炸棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the acceleration of gravity gets the non-explosive rod
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在撞击时的速度超过了时速1万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}moving at more than 10,000 miles an hour by the time of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着我们能够让越来越重的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As we're able to get heavier and heavier objects
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动的速度越来越快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}moving at faster and faster velocities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能打击东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it starts to become possible to hit things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有原子弹的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the energy of an atomic bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不必实际用上任何的辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without actually having to use any sort of radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重的金属棒穿透月球岩层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The heavy metal rod penetrates layers of Moon rock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去摧毁地下指挥中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to destroy the underground command center.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需爆炸 单凭动能就足以摧毁该地区了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Without explosives, kinetic energy aIone has devastated the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如小行星 产生巨大的弹坑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like an asteroid, creating a huge crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而不管太空武器会变得如何先进\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But no matter how advanced space weapons become,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争与技术上的一个基本原则\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of the basic principles of warfare and technology
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会依然适用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will probably still apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为人性与人类史上一个不可避免的事实\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l think it's an inevitable fact of human nature and human history
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种武器的发明与使用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the invention of one weapon and its use
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会引发对策 或试图致胜的方法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}triggers a countermeasure or a way to try to defeat it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或打造更好的武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or build a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你会看到在太空武器中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you're going to see that in space weaponry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不介意你在未来走得多远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}no matter how far in the future you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付定向能武器的一个绝妙对策\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A fantastic countermeasure against a directed-energy weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如激光那样的 将会是隐形装置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like, say, a laser, would be a cloaking device
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸如我们在科幻电影《星际迷航》里屡见不鲜的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like we see in many science fiction shows like "Star Trek."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们能让飞船隐形\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we can render a ship invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么电磁能就只能擦肩而过了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then electromagnetic energy just passes right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过让整个飞船隐形的技术\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the technology to make entire spaceships invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或让激光有足够强大到远距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or the power needed to create lasers strong enough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击中大目标所需的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to blast big targets from vast distances
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将远远超出了我们目前的能力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are well beyond our current capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前 尚没有任何进攻性武器驻扎在太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And right now, there aren't any offensive weapons stationed in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在未来十年左右的时间里 战争仍然可能进入太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But war could still come to space within the next decade or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的太空战争可能看起来有所不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The future of space warfare may look a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始 我想会是卫星与反卫星系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At first, I think it's going to be satellites and anti-satellite systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹与卫星 都是不载人的系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}missiles and satellites, not manned systems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么卫星及摧毁它们的武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And why would satellites and weapons that could destroy them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是太空战争一开始的重点呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}likely be the focus of the first space war?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为卫星已经是地面战争必不可少的了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because satellites are already essential to fighting wars on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国尤其极度依赖太空了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}America, in particular, is extremely dependent on space.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的军队如今离开了卫星已无法运作了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our military cannot operate the way it does today without satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将它们用于通讯 导航\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We use them for communications, navigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜集各种情报\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}intelligence gathering of all kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是图像情报还是信号情报\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whether it's photo intelligence, whether it's signal intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量都是靠卫星来完成的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a lot of it is done by satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至地面机动都需要非常精准的定位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even ground maneuvers require very accurate positioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPS信号\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}GPS signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2007年以来 中美两国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Since 2007, China and the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都证明了他们有能力用导弹来摧毁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have proven they're capable of destroying satellites
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低地球轨道卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in low-Earth orbit with missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们各自清除了自己的一颗卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They've each taken out one of their own satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝非易事 因为卫星在空中飞驰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's no easy feat since the satellites are streaking across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上空数百英里高处 时速达到了约1 7万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a few hundred miles above Earth at about 17,000 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有快速计算机 人们是没有任何可能的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Without fast computers, people wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用导弹击中太空中的卫星 难度不亚于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hitting a satellite in space with a missile is as difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的网球去击中别人发出的网球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as hitting someone else's tennis serve with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把握正确的时间 把握正确的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Getting the timing, getting the speed right,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是难以办到的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's virtually impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对于具有先进技术的现代导弹而言\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But for a modern missile with advanced technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就并不那么困难了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's not that difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些导弹的传感器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}These missiles have sensors
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们确定自己的位置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that allow them to determine their own location
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标的位置及其变化\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the target location and changes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间调整并击中它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and make split-second adjustments and hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设想一下 要是你有一个聪明的网球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Imagine if you had a smart tennis ball
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用上类似的传感技术\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}using the same kind of sensor technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每秒钟调整位置数百次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}adjusting its location hundreds of times a second
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来确保其击中目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make sure it hit the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹拦截卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And once a missile intercepts a satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爆炸是不需要的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a big explosion isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 许多反卫星导弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, many anti-satellite missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都设计成简单撞击其目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are designed to simply ram their target
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无需任何爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without any explosives at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于太空的材料被设计成非常轻质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Space-based materials are designed to be fairly light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物体送上轨道花费不菲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's very expensive to lift things into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要上百磅燃料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It takes about a hundred pounds of fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能将一磅东西送入轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to lift one pound into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你会尽可能将东西做轻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you want to make things as light as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也使得它们通常比较容易毁坏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which makes them also usually comparatively easy to knock out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地球上 一场全面太空战争的影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And back on Earth, the effects of an all-out space war
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在未来十年里将十分严峻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the next decade would be severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果各国开始相互间摧毁空中的卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If countries begin blasting each other's satellites out of the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题很快就会蔓延开来 远不止使其难以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the problems would quickly spread beyond making it difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对发动战争的军事卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the military to wage war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的全球科技绝对依赖太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today's global society is definitely dependent on space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们失去卫星 不光是军事卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we were to start losing satellites, not just military satellites,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有通讯和民用卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but commercial and civil satellites,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么日常生活将会如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what would happen to daily life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间 ATM机罢工了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Suddenly, ATM machines don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多手机罢工了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Many cell phones don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自助加油不工作了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Pay at the pump no longer works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的金融业务\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Financial transactions all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用的GPS计时信号突然间都中断了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that use the GPS timing signal all of a sudden are disrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个世界放慢了脚步\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the whole world slows down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太空战争升级到完全失控\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if a space war escalated totally out of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹可能会携带核弹头进入太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}missiles might carry nuclear warheads into space
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以确保重要目标在大爆炸中消灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make sure important targets were knocked out with a big blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你不会相信太空核爆炸的样子有何不同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But you won't believe how different a nuclear blast in space looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及它仍然会对地球造成破坏程度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and how destructive it can still be back on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的武器库里有一件武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's one weapon in today's arsenals
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还会在未来的大规模太空战争中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that might still be used to annihilate targets
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来消灭目标 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in massive space battles of the future:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}atomic bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过曾经见过地球上的原子弹爆炸的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But anyone used to seeing atomic explosions on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很难认出这些太空中的爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would have a hard time recognizing these blasts in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空核爆炸一个毛骨悚然的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the creepy things about exploding a nuclear weapon in space
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它看上去并不是你想象的那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is it doesn't look like anything you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上 我们会看到这种标志性的蘑菇云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here on the planet Earth, we see this iconic mushroom cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在太空中 由于没有大气 所以也就没有云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But in space, with no atmosphere, there's no cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反 你会有一个扩散的辐射气泡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Instead you have an expanding bubble of radiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个闪光 像星星一样 很小 变成了超新星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a single flash of light like a star, very small, going supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最初的几纳秒里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the first few nanoseconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:14:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高能伽玛射线随着一道闪光向四处爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}high-energy gamma rays explode in all directions along with a flash of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧接着是扩散的辐射云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}followed by an expanding cloud of radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上撕碎建筑物的冲击波不见了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The shockwave that rips buildings apart on Earth is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太空中没有空气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}since there's no atmosphere in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是辐射扩散的范围比地球上更快更广\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the sphere of radiation expands faster and farther than on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就能想到的几乎就像是子弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can just think of almost like bullets,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是它们是辐射粒子的飞出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but they're radiation particles going out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会源源不断的流出 - 伽玛射线 中子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they will travel a long ways-- gamma rays, neutrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会穿透卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They will penetrate satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些刚好经过爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some go blasting right through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它会打击电子元件 造成很大的危害\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Others hit electronics and cause a lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于平均规模的核弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With an average-size nuclear bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半径50英里范围内的任何卫星都将被摧毁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}any satellites within a 50-mile radius will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而太空核爆炸不仅仅破坏设备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But an atomic blast in space wouldn't just destroy equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员飞经太空核爆炸产生的碎片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronauts flying through the debris from an exploded nuclear weapon in space
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会遭遇极端的辐射量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be subject to extreme levels of radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是 放射性核的放射性衰变\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In particular, there are gamma rays
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会产生出伽玛射线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}coming from radioactive decay of radioactive nuclei,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会与皮肤发生作用 引发癌症\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they can interact with skin and cause cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有高能电子和其他粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Also there are energetic electrons and other particles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来自这些放射性核\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}coming from these radioactive nuclei,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有这些东西会危害生命组织\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all of these things are damaging to living tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有风或其它空气影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Without any wind or other atmospheric effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辐射的扩散范围\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that expanding sphere of radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会数月保持在危险水平上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would stay at dangerous levels for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的导弹可能会携带核弹头进入太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today's missiles can carry nuclear warheads into space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为原子弹会与地球上部的大气层产生互动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and due to the way atomic bombs interact with Earth's upper atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个国家可以用太空爆炸来解决另一个国家的目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one country might decide to target another with a blast in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它实际上会造成很大的破坏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because it actually causes a lot of damage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路到地球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the way down on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当核武器在地球大气层最高处爆炸时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When a nuclear weapon goes off above most of the Earth's atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会释放出伽玛射线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it releases a bunch of gamma rays,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极高能的电磁辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}very high-energy electromagnetic radiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电离大气层里的大气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that ionize the gas in the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 它们会踢走原子和分子里的电子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that is, they kick the electrons off of the atoms and molecules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些电子主要是踢向地面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those electrons are kicked largely in a downward direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度会接近光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they're moving at a substantial fraction of the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 它产生了一个极大的电流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, that creates an incredible electric current,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够对地球上的弟子设备产生很大的电压差\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that can set up big voltage differences
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和很大的电涌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and big surges of current in electrical equipment here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果美国是目标的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if America were the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会有突然的电流峰 即所谓的电磁脉冲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there'd be a sudden spike of current known as an electromagnetic pulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}EMP\Nor EMP,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落下就像是个巨大的无形闪电球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}coming down like a massive invisible ball of lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会瞬间破坏电子设备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It destroys electronics
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和任何带有电流的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and anything else carrying an electric current in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的核爆炸也会产生EMP\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Atomic blasts on Earth also create EMPs,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是范围极其有限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but with more limited ranges.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而大气层上方的爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By exploding above the atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个核爆炸就能够摧毁一个国家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a single atomic blast could devastate the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据估计 如果你在堪萨斯州上空100公里处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's been estimated that if you lit off
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引爆一个百万吨级的核弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a one-megaton nuclear weapon 100 kilometers over Kansas,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会令美国大部分 如果不是全部的电子设备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you would render most, if not all the electronics
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失效\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the United States inoperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空核爆炸对地球的破坏不只是理论上的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The damage on Earth from atomic explosions in space isn't just theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始于上世纪50年代后期 冷战高峰时期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Starting in the late 1950s, during the height of the Cold War,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国及前苏联\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}both the United States and the former Soviet Union
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了唯一利用太空作为核试验场的国家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}became the only nations to use space as a nuclear testing ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1962年在太平洋上空进行的最后一次试验\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the last tests in 1962 above the Pacific Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生的EMP毁坏的电子设备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}created an EMP that knocked out electronics
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从新西兰一直到夏威夷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the way from New Zealand to Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以影响很大的区域 用这些电流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you can affect a large area with these currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些瞬间电流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}these sharp currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是在核弹下方直接影响的区域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not just the immediate area right below the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在太空中和地球上的广泛破坏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because of the widespread damage in space and on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个国家在十来次试验后都停止了这些爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}both countries stopped these blasts after less than two dozen tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了预防不确定的大核爆打击无害的卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To avoid hitting friendly satellites or spacecraft with big, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和航天器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}imprecise nuclear blasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常规武器可以被用于太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}conventional firearms could be used in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你在空间站外负责防卫的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if you were in charge of security outside of a space station,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通手枪在微重力环境中 没有大气中的氧气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would a normal handgun even fire without atmospheric oxygen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开火吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a microgravity environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火药里头自己带有氧化剂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gunpowder has its own oxidizer built into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能够开火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so it would fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你设法让撞针打击子弹的屁股\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you managed to get the firing pin to hit the end of the bullet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就会开火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it would go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在它会不会弹出滑槽 下一颗子弹入膛？ \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now would it eject the slide and the next bullet go into the round
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会那样动作吗？ 这是个好问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and would that work? That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不能肯定 在它卡壳停止工作之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm not real positive that it would fire more than a few times
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开火几次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before it seized up and quit working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题很大部分在于枪里的金属活动部件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A big part of the problem is that the metal moving parts inside guns
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要润滑油才能工作顺畅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}need lubricants to work smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是极端严酷的太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but the harsh extremes of space
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会导致润滑油失效\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would probably cause the lubricants to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举个例子 比如手枪置于阳光下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If a handgun got in the sunlight, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变得很热很热\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it would get really, really hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部件可能会粘在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the parts would seize together probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是在阳光下 就会变得很冷很冷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If it were not in the sunlight, it would get really, really cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部件也可能会粘在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the parts would seize together probably,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,润滑油在真空的太空中很难发挥作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and lubricants just have a hard time of working in the vacuum of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的问题是它们会结珠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The biggest problem is they bead up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会变成小珠子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They turn into little balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有重力 没有空气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because there's no gravity or any other atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使其能够依附\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that it can adhere to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇航员在微重力下饮液体时已证实了同样的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronauts have demonstrated the same thing when they drink liquids in microgravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是连贯地流出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Instead of flowing evenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,液体而是分开形成一连串的小球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the liquids separate into a series of spheres.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一个系统会工作良好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there is one system that would work well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来防范太空中的歹徒 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for keeping away the bad guys in space:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用轨道炮来发射炮弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}launching bullets with a rail gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道炮用一个强磁场系列\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Rail guns use a series of strong magnetic fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是用火药来推进炮弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}rather than gunpowder, to propel bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的轨道炮炮弹已经能够发射到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Current rail gun projectiles can already race downrange
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M16步枪射出的子弹的三倍快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about three times faster than a bullet from an M-16 rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道炮的概念就是你将小弹丸 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The idea of a rail gun is you take a small pellet that's 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是金属的 有可能是塑料的 不管什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It may be metal, it may be plastic, may be whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你必须将它包在铝箔里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but you have to have it wrapped in aluminum foil,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你要在两根长轨之间完成一个电路\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because you complete an electric circuit between two long rails
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造磁场来加速在轨道端部的小弹丸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the magnetic field created accelerates that little pellet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能够将其加速得很快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}out the end of the rails, and it can accelerate it very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高 有人认为 可以接近光速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Up to, some people believe, close to the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似的系统应用于\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Similar systems are at work
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些高铁和过山车上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in certain bullet trains and roller coasters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一系列的磁铁 磁铁驱动物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have a series of magnets, and the magnets propel an object,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是过山车还是你想用它来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}either a roller coaster car or this giant slug of a bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击太空中的东西巨大的子弹棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you want to use to hit something in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一头到另一头 不断将其加速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from one to the other, accelerating as it goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦它经过了一定数量的加速器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and by the time it's reached a certain number of accelerators,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定数量的磁铁对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a certain number of pairs of magnets,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就会达到你所需要的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's really going as fast as you need it to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安装在大型航天器上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mounted on a large spacecraft,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道炮有可能成为未来的舰载大炮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the rail gun could become the naval cannon of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长长排列的强大磁铁能够推动大炮弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Long rows of powerful magnets could propel big projectiles
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时速数百万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to millions of miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那种大炮是否足以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But would that kind of gun be enough
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外星文明毁灭地球之前将其消灭呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to take out an alien civilization before it could destroy Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今百年后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A hundred years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参战的飞船可能会用超高速轨道炮来开火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}spaceships at war may blast away with ultra-high-speed rail guns
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需炸药去摧毁目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that destroy targets without explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要以时速数千乃至百万英里的速度来攻击敌人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just by slamming into the enemy at many thousands or even millions of miles an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会释放出巨量的动能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they'll release incredible amounts of kinetic energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the energy of motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2008年 美国海军测试了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In 2008, the U.S. Navy tested
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现存最强大的轨道炮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the most powerful rail gun that now exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用一系列磁铁和强大的电流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Using a series of magnets and strong electrical currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它发射了一个7磅重的炮弹 时速超过了5000英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it launched a 7-pound projectile at over 5,000 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大炮估计全程运作的射程将达到200英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The gun's estimated range when fully operational will be 200 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮弹的速度是音速的七倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A slug moving at seven times the speed of sound
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会造成很大的破坏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}does a lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是你很高兴我们所掌握的那些东西之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's one of those things where you're glad it's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种武器确实能够对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the kind of weapon that could really do some damage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野蛮外星文明的都市造成某种破坏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the capital city of a violent alien civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以想象巨型母舰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can envision the big mother ship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,携带沿着船边运行的轨道炮 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}having a rail gun that runs along the periphery
