Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.71,0:28:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能排列整齐 走出腔膛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is lined up and coming out of the chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.09,0:28:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同类型的激光能够以不同的方式破坏目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And different types of lasers can damage targets in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.97,0:28:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦福大学的高能激光实验室里的这种绿色激光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This green-light laser at Stanford University's high-power laser lab
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.26,0:28:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉冲的开闭是强大的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}pulses on and off in powerful bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.10,0:28:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它实际上并不产生大量的热量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's actually not delivering a lot of heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.19,0:28:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 它是一个很强的电场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What it is, though, is a very strong electric field.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.90,0:29:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以提供一个足够强的电场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And this one can provide a strong enough electric field.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过创造一个强电场 你就可以撕开原子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By creating a high electric field, you can rip apart atoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以将电子剥离原子 如果你愿意的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you can rip electrons off of atoms if you wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.86,0:29:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以分解物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you can break down materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.99,0:29:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强电场甚至还可以撕碎大气分子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The strong electrical field even rips apart air molecules.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.91,0:29:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们在各个脉冲之间同时回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They come back together between each pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.62,0:29:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时你就会看到这种闪光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that's when you get this flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.79,0:29:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在能量释放时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}'cause when the energy comes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.25,0:29:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会看到光 会收到那边的报告\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you see the light, and you get the report that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.13,0:29:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如雷电\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}much like thunder and lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.30,0:29:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些强电场尤其擅长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And these strong fields are especially good
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.14,0:29:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏电子设备\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at knocking out electronic equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 激光束非常强大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, the laser beam is so powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.18,0:29:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上会破坏我们拍摄这些画面的摄像机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it actually damaged our camera as we recorded these images
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.15,0:29:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦尘埃粒子偏转部分脉冲到镜头里的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when dust particles deflected part of the pulse into the lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.90,0:29:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它留下了一个永恒的绿色印记\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It left a permanent green imprint
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.86,0:29:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在摄像机的聚光CCD屏幕上了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on the camera's light-gathering CCD imager.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.28,0:29:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验室的另一台激光演示了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another laser at the lab demonstrates
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.53,0:29:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续脉冲波的威力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the power of continuous waves instead of pulses.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.83,0:29:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个红外光束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's an infrared beam,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.21,0:29:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此肉眼是看不见的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so it's not visible to the human eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.46,0:30:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其影响是显而易见的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but its effects certainly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.13,0:30:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它非常类似于军方目前在开发的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's very similar to the one that military is developing,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.67,0:30:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是军方的要强大5万倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}only the military's is about 50,000 times stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.64,0:30:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我们有一个透镜 我们只要穿过透镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right here we have a lens, and so as we go through the lens,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.06,0:30:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束就会聚焦到这个平面上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the beam is focusing down in this plane here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.98,0:30:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在那个面上放上一个靶子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I put a target in that plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.85,0:30:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以看到我们最终让它燃烧 因为有热量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you can see that we end up burning it because of the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.57,0:30:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我可以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I can then take out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.15,0:30:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这张卡片上取下一片精美光滑的切片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a nice, smoothly edged piece of cardboard from this cardstock.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.82,0:30:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来太空战里的激光武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The laser weapons of future space wars
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.62,0:30:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的功能大同小异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would likely work in the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.62,0:30:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是科幻电影迷们可能会惊讶地发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but sci-fi movie fans may be very surprised to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.08,0:30:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的激光武器在太空中的作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how real laser weapons will actually work in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.79,0:30:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在科幻片中 我们经常看到激光闪电\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In science fiction, we often see a laser bolt,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.88,0:30:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量光束 然而在现实中 对于激光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a bolt of energy, whereas in reality, with a laser,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.13,0:30:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是看不到光束闪烁的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you'd see a beam connect, then disconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.05,0:30:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 光是我们所知道最快的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l mean, light is the fastest thing we know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.48,0:31:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看到有人用激光束对准你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you were to see someone about to shoot you with a laser beam,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就必须快速做出反应\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you would have to react very quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.94,0:31:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你看到他们的手指要去扳动按钮的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when you see their finger beginning to twitch toward the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.69,0:31:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Otherwise, 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.55,0:31:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会在看到敌人启动武器的同时遭毒手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you'll get zapped at the same time that you see the zapper initiate the zapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.49,0:31:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在决斗在真空的太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But in a duel in the vacuum of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.24,0:31:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是利用可见光的激光武器的光束都是看不见的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even the beams of laser weapons using visible light won't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.25,0:31:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里可以看到这个光束的原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the reason that we can see this beam here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.30,0:31:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在于它被空气中的尘埃给散射了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that it's scattering off of the dust particles in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.59,0:31:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空中 不存在尘埃粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In space, there are no dust particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.76,0:31:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是真空的 所以你无法看到光束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a vacuum, so you wouldn't see the beam,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.14,0:31:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了抵达了目标并从目标反射回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}except for at its target and reflections off of its target.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.44,0:31:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为声音无法在真空中穿行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And since sound can't travel through a vacuum,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.27,0:31:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此没有那些很酷的科幻音效\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}none of those cool sci-fi laser sound effects
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.07,0:31:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将属于真实的太空激光战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be part of a real laser battle in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.12,0:31:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即使太空激光武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even though laser weapons in space
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.28,0:31:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模样和声音并不像它们在电影里那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}won't look and sound like they do in the movies,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.95,0:32:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们在战场上还是迅猛致命的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they'll still be fast and deadly on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.92,0:32:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么真正的太空空战又是何种样子呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what will a real space dogfight look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.25,0:32:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼见为实\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You'll have to see it to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.05,0:32:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种武器能超过高能激光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No weapon has fascinated generations of science fiction fans
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.22,0:32:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让代代科幻迷们如痴如醉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}more than high-energy lasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.48,0:32:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能不久 在未来的数十年里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's possible that as soon as the next few decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.15,0:32:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光将强大到足以在一眨眼间 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lasers will be powerful enough to knock out satellites 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.09,0:32:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击毁近地卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in near-Earth orbit in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.07,0:32:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有武器能快过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No weapon is faster than 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.06,0:32:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度为每秒186万英里的激光束\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a laser's beam of light traveling at 186,000 miles per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.33,0:32:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们能打造出一种武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If we could build a weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.50,0:32:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有洞穿装甲钢板的能力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that had the capabilities to punch through armor plating,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.17,0:32:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你真的找到好东东了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then you really are onto something,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:33:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果它就是你用来驱动物体的电能的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because if it is just electrical power that you need to drive the thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.93,0:33:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就有了我们所谓的无限弹仓了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you have what we call an infinite magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.31,0:33:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你提及战舰上的大炮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you're talking about the big gun on a battleship,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.90,0:33:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须要有炮弹和火药\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you have to have bullets and gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.53,0:33:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会耗尽它们的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can run out of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.11,0:33:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你只是用电能来打造一个激光系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you simply use electrical power to create a laser system,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.87,0:33:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就无庸担心谁给我们送来更多的炮弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we don't have to worry about somebody bringing us more bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.54,0:33:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在哪里储存那些炮弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and where to store those bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.29,0:33:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于地球上的激光武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Laser weapons for use on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.42,0:33:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能随时出现在战场上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may begin showing up on battlefields any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.97,0:33:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在2008到2009年间 美国空军\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In 2008 and 2009, the United States Air Force
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.18,0:33:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一种武器进行了有限的测试 就是所谓的机载激光系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}conducted limited tests with a weapon known as the Airborne Laser System.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.02,0:33:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从改装的波音747头部射出的高能激光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a high-energy laser fired from the nose of a modified Boeing 747
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.69,0:33:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能识别并跟踪目标\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that identifies and tracks targets
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.32,0:33:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样它就能用精准的能量束去击毁它们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so it can blast them with a precise beam of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.03,0:34:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以发出巨大的激光能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It can put an awful lot of laser energy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.08,0:34:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机在高空飞行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The airplane flies at high altitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.29,0:34:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以瞄准并消灭导弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it can shoot up and take out missiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.42,0:34:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它是个反导弹系统\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so it's a counter-missile system.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.05,0:34:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为期不远了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the day is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.30,0:34:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着技术让我们将激光器封装在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As technology allows us to package lasers
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.47,0:34:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越小的系统里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in smaller and smaller systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.22,0:34:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就可以将它们放上卫星 理论上可以消灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we can put them on satellites and theoretically take out missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.02,0:34:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大气层外闯入的导弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}coming up out of the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.31,0:34:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于其达到光速的惊人能力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And with their speed-of-light striking ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.11,0:34:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光将会是宇航战士的杰出武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lasers would be a great weapon for spaceship fighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.53,0:34:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过未来的飞船之间的空战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But futuristic dogfights between spacecraft
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会与现在的空战\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will have little in common with today's aerial battles
