Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.66,0:38:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你会做得方式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That would be the way you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即使有人驾驶的太空战斗机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But even though piloted space fighters
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.54,0:39:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能不是未来的主要武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may not be a dominant weapon in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.63,0:39:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光在太空战中仍可能发挥作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lasers are still likely to play a role if war comes to space,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.17,0:39:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管它们还有一些挑战需要克服\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}although they will have some challenges to overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.60,0:39:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后30年 地球上的地面站\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}30 years from now, a ground station on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.56,0:39:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正试图用激光去摧毁敌方的卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is trying to destroy an enemy satellite with a laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.64,0:39:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在其抵达其目标之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But before it reaches its target,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.73,0:39:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束将不得不应付地球的大气层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the beam will have to deal with Earth's atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.73,0:39:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是曾经将吸管放入过一杯水里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you've ever stuck a straw into a glass of water
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.65,0:39:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从侧面去观察\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and looked at it from the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.11,0:39:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能已经注意到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you might have noticed that 
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.60,0:39:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸管在穿过水面时弯曲了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the straw appears to bend as it goes through the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.70,0:39:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为光从一种材料穿到另一种材料时被弯曲了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is because light gets bent as it goes through one material and into another.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.33,0:39:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光穿越我们的大气层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, lasers passing through our atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.17,0:39:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将不得不面对同样的问题 - 折射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have to deal with the same sort of problem--refraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.42,0:39:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此如果我们试图将激光从地球表面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So when we're trying to point lasers
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.01,0:39:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指向太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the surfaces of the Earth, out into space,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.93,0:39:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就必须考虑到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we have to take into consideration
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气层会多大程度弯曲光线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how much the atmosphere bends light.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.14,0:40:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已在太空中的激光武器会更为有效地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A laser weapon already in space will be much more effective
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.61,0:40:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭卫星或航天器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at taking out satellites or spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.28,0:40:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空高处 没有空气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Up in space, there would be no atmosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.57,0:40:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而没有激光的衰减\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and so there'd be no attenuation of the laser light,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.20,0:40:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在穿越大气时会发生的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as there is when it's going through the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.62,0:40:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除非科学家拿出一个强劲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But until scientists come up with a strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.92,0:40:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻质的能源供太空里使用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lightweight energy source for use in space,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.75,0:40:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则激光将不会强大到能炸掉任何东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lasers won't be powerful enough to blast anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.42,0:40:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的能量限制\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the same kind of energy limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.72,0:40:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将有可能将激光武器排斥在太空战士的双手之外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will likely keep laser weapons out of the hands of space soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.64,0:40:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我们创造一个核聚变装置在手机大小的电池里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Until we create a fusion reactor in a cell phone-sized battery,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.06,0:40:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是不会携带那种东西随时去搞破坏的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're not going to be carrying those things around anytime soon that do real damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.32,0:40:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像科克船长的手持光炮 狂轰滥炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like Captain Kirk's hand-held phaser, that he shoots and destroys
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.61,0:40:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人整个撕碎\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and completely disintegrates somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.99,0:41:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那需要大量的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That takes a lot of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.66,0:41:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道里头究竟是什么能源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd like to know what power source those things have in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.21,0:41:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是激光结果并不是未来主要的太空武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if lasers don't turn out to be the dominant space weapon of the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.75,0:41:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么百年以后月球表面的的战斗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then what might a battle on the surface of the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会是何种模样呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}look like 100 years from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.05,0:41:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为殖民地之间经常会发生争执\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As colonies often do, they get into a dispute
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.68,0:41:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生一些战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and have some kind of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.76,0:41:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会觉得很唐突的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You would think it would be fairly short.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.26,0:41:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环境一开始就充满敌意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The environment is so hostile to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.18,0:41:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你庆幸还活着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you're lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.98,0:41:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近敌对殖民地的攻击力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The attacking force approaching the rival colony
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.94,0:41:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许相当小 源于严酷的环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will probably be fairly small, due to the harsh conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.82,0:41:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及将人及装备送入太空的巨大成本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the huge cost of bringing people and equipment into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.95,0:41:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于同样的节约成本的原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And for the same cost-saving reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.70,0:41:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地也是用轻质材料打造的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the colony will also be made from lightweight, thin materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.58,0:41:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送不锈钢或其它重型装甲 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It costs way too much to send stainless steel 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.77,0:41:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花费太昂贵了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or whatever would be heavy armored plating.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.76,0:41:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是首批殖民地会做得事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's not what the first colonies are going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.72,0:41:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会非常脆弱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're going to be very fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.22,0:42:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此即使是简单的攻击也会非常有效\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So even a simple attack could be very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.22,0:42:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你只会看到有人拉着炸弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think you would just find somebody trucking a bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.77,0:42:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去错误的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}over to the wrong place
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.06,0:42:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄潜入 将其引爆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and sneaking it in and setting it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.48,0:42:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或对人发射一颗小导弹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or launching a small missile at somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.36,0:42:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那确实很难阻止的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be incredibly hard to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.86,0:42:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会极其容易把人们杀死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would be incredibly easy to get everybody killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.74,0:42:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是攻击力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if the strike force
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.91,0:42:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能立马将殖民地消灭\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}isn't able to take out the colony right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.54,0:42:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就有可能面临来自月球表面的反击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they might face a counterattack out on the surface of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.08,0:42:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 在真空的太空里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here, in the vacuum of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.75,0:42:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是最小的伤口都可以让人送命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even the smallest wound can be a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果宇航服被打出一个洞 就会漏气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If a hole were punched in a spacesuit, it would leak,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.60,0:42:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 洞穿宇航服的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and by the way, what punched the hole in the spacesuit
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.27,0:42:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准会一路洞穿里面的人 不是吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}probably kept on punching through to the person inside it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.60,0:42:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你如何去救助那个人呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So how do you help that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.73,0:42:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如何对他们急救呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How do you perform first aid on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.61,0:42:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过遥远未来的太空战争\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the space wars of the distant future
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.11,0:43:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能超越人与机器的整个技术\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may move beyond the technology of man and machine altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.87,0:43:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟 宇宙自然现象的破坏力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After all, the destructive power of natural phenomena in the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.54,0:43:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远超过人类所制造的任何武器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}goes far beyond any weapon people have ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展望未来数百年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Looking hundreds of years into the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.17,0:43:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好战的外星文明正利用火星作为中转区\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a belligerent alien civilization is using Mars as a staging area
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.30,0:43:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备入侵地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for their coming invasion of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.81,0:43:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们可以设想重新定位一颗小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One might imagine redirecting an asteroid
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.31,0:43:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或飞经太阳系的石块\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or a rock flying through the solar system,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.81,0:43:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让其去撞击火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that it hits Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.90,0:43:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以设想发射火箭到小行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We could imagine firing a rocket to an asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.15,0:43:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍偏转其轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}deflecting it ever so slightly in its trajectory,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.28,0:43:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样经过数次转轨 它就会最终撞上火星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that after a number of orbits, it would finally hit Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.17,0:43:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而是不是人们免不了会把\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But is it inevitable that man will turn
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.34,0:43:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终的边界变成战场的呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the final frontier into a battleground?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.46,0:44:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或我们在破坏性技术上的进步是否会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or could our advances in destructive technology
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.67,0:44:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匹配上理智和自我保护的进步呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}be matched by advances in wisdom and self-preservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.51,0:44:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类总是觉得不久的将来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Human beings always think that one day soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.35,0:44:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会超越冲突的需求\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we're going to move beyond the need for conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.81,0:44:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里没做到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We haven't done it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.44,0:44:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为我们在太空中会超越它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I don't think we're going to move beyond it in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.65,0:44:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上多数国家已经签署了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most countries of the world have already signed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.49,0:44:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众所周知的1967外太空条约\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what's commonly known as the 1967 Outer Space Treaty,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.24,0:44:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留太空 月球 其他行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}preserving space, the Moon, and other planets
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.21,0:44:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于和平目的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for peaceful purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.67,0:44:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但随着未来的太空旅行越来越常态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But as space travel in the future becomes more routine
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.13,0:44:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有价值的未开发资源\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and if valuable untapped resources
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.46,0:44:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球外发现 一个条约管用吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are discovered beyond Earth, will a treaty be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.22,0:44:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有时间才能证明这种奇特的太空武器库\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Only time will tell if this arsenal of exotic space weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.18,0:44:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是我们未来的预演\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a preview of our future
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.18,0:44:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我们的庸人自扰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or a dangerous fantasy world.
